channel.title: Symon's Dinners Cooking Out
channel.desc: Michael Symon turns the flavors of ranch dressing into a rub for ranch-rubbed pork ribs; he also uses it in baked sweet potatoes with charred onion ranch dip; Michael's wife, Liz, makes grilled corn with ranchovy butter, featuring the rub yet again.
